'''迈克·泰勒'''（{{lang-en|'''Maik Taylor'''}}，{{bd|1971年|9月4日|catIdx=Taylor, Maik}}），前[[北愛爾蘭|北愛爾蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[守門員|守門員]]。自2019年6月起，於[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英格蘭足球乙級聯賽]]球隊[[沃爾索爾足球俱樂部|沃爾索爾]]擔任守門員教練<ref>[https://www.saddlers.co.uk/news/2019/june/maik-taylor-announced-a-new-goalkeeping-coach/ Maik Taylor appointed as new goalkeeping coach]</ref>。

==球會生平==

米克·泰萊於1997年由[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|修咸頓]]加盟[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]，協助球隊從第四級的[[英格蘭足球聯賽|丙組]]升級到[[英超|英超]]。2001年7月富咸從[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|祖雲達斯]]收購[[埃德文·范德萨|雲達沙]]，米克泰萊的正選地位不保<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/northern_ireland/1467614.stm |title=Taylor Premiership hopes in doubt |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307032434/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/northern_ireland/1467614.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月米克泰萊透露希望離開富咸<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/northern_ireland/1656218.stm Taylor to quit the Cottage]</ref>。但12月雲達沙因斷腳而長期缺陣，米克泰萊重獲正選並且有出色的表現<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/2864395.stm |title=Taylor could quit Cottagers |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307005602/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/f/fulham/2864395.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2003年8月8日米克·泰萊以外借身份加盟[[伯明翰足球俱乐部|伯明翰城]]一年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3126051.stm |title=Blues finally land Taylor |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619115538/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3126051.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2004年3月22日他與球會簽下正式合約，轉會費150萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約至2008年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3547587.stm |title=Blues seal Taylor deal |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307164417/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3547587.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他加盟伯明翰後一直有非常穩定的發揮<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3592705.stm |title=Bruce salutes Taylor |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307195231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3592705.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3628789.stm |title=Bruce in Taylor tribute |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307040416/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/3628789.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，獲選2003/04年球季北愛爾蘭FWA國際球員<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/3698221.stm |title=Blues dominate awards |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307033925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/3698221.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且入選了英超最佳陣容。

2007年初[[科林·多伊尔|-{zh-hans:科林·多伊尔; zh-hk:杜爾;}-]]一度取代米克·泰萊在伯明翰城的正選位置<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/6582831.stm |title=Doyle signs new Birmingham deal |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307005022/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/6582831.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但在重返[[英超|英超]]後的伯明翰城再次起用米克·泰萊擔任正選<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6931067.stm |title=Chelsea 3-2 Birmingham |accessdate=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619065627/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6931067.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年6月14日米克泰萊續約兩年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7453823.stm |title=Taylor agrees new Birmingham deal |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307185707/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/b/birmingham_city/7453823.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]伯明翰城從[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]借用[[乔·哈特|祖·赫特]]，整季一直佔據正選席位，米克·泰萊僅在聯賽上陣兩場，均是對祖·赫特因借用條款未能上陣的母會曼城。[[2010年至2011年英格蘭超級聯賽|翌季]]伯明翰城又從另一支[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]球隊[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]正式羅致[[賓·科士打_(足球運動員)|-{zh-hans:本·福斯特;zh-hk:賓·科士打;}-]]，季初續約一年的米克·泰萊繼續擔任板凳球員，僅獲派在盃賽上陣4場，但在[[2011年英格蘭聯賽盃決賽|聯賽盃決賽]]亦只能屈居後備席廂。隨著球隊於球季結束後降班，米克·泰萊成為6名約滿被放棄的球員之一<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13573178.stm |title=Relegated Birmingham confirm exit of six players |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-27 |accessdate=2011-11-25 |archive-date=2011-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111124213648/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13573178.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年11月24日年屆40歲的米克·泰萊以短約形式加盟[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，為期至翌年1月<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/9646810.stm |title=Leeds United bring in goalkeeper Maik Taylor |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-11-24 |accessdate=2011-11-25 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022213137/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/9646810.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。未有機會為列斯聯上陣，米克·泰萊於2012年3月12日獲緊急借用到另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[米尔沃尔足球俱乐部|米禾爾]]直至球季結束<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17340145 |title=Millwall sign Leeds United goalkeeper Maik Taylor |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2012-03-12 |accessdate=2012-03-13 |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314205537/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17340145 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==國家隊==
米克泰萊的父親是[[英國|英國]]人，而母親是[[德國|德國]]人<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/4607577.stm |title=Family ties for Taylor at Windsor |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307031005/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/irish/4607577.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，由於在海外出生而領取[[英國|英國]][[護照|護照]]，因而可以選擇代表[[聯合王國|聯合王國]]中任何一地，曾是[[北愛爾蘭足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭]]的常規門將，只有[[萊·卡路爾|-{zh-hans:罗伊·卡罗尔; zh-hk:卡路爾;}-]]（Roy Carroll）對他的地位稍有威脅<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5412326.stm |title=Taylor eyes start against Danes |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307133024/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5412326.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。代表出賽超過80次。於1999年首次披上國家隊球衣出戰[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]，以0-3見負。2008年8月20日作客對[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]，因隊長[[艾朗·曉士|艾朗·曉士]]受傷缺陣，米克泰萊獲選戴上隊長臂章<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7571078.stm |title=Taylor to captain NI in Glasgow |access-date=2008-08-20 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307042115/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7571078.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

